tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE customs_data (
    customs_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    import_country VARCHAR(255),
    export_country VARCHAR(255),
    item_description TEXT,
    item_value DECIMAL(10, 2),
    tariff_code VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE customs_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customs_office VARCHAR(255),
  import_activity VARCHAR(255),
  export_activity VARCHAR(255),
  tariff DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE tariffs (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  tariff_code VARCHAR(10),
  description TEXT,
  country_origin VARCHAR(255),
  country_destination VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE import_activities (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  import_id UUID,
  imported_item VARCHAR(255),
  import_date DATE,
  import_customs_code VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE export_activities (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  export_id UUID,
  exported_item VARCHAR(255),
  export_date DATE,
  export_customs_code VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE customs_data (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  import_country VARCHAR(255),
  export_country VARCHAR(255),
  shipment_id UUID,
  customs_status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE tariffs (
  tariff_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  country VARCHAR(255),
  product_name VARCHAR(255),
  tariff_rate DECIMAL(5, 2),
  effective_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE import_activities (
  import_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  import_date DATE,
  imported_product VARCHAR(255),
  quantity INTEGER,
  customs_clearance_status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE export_activities (
  export_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  export_date DATE,
  exported_product VARCHAR(255),
  destination_country VARCHAR(255),
  shipping_status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Customs_Data (
	entry_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	importer_name VARCHAR(255),
	exporter_name VARCHAR(255),
	shipment_qty INT,
	shipment_value DECIMAL(10, 2),
	customs_clearance_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Import_Activities (
	import_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	entry_id INT,
	import_date DATE,
	import_quantity INT,
	from_country VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE Export_Activities (
	export_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	entry_id INT,
	export_date DATE,
	export_quantity INT,
	to_country VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE Countries (
	country_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	country_name VARCHAR(255),
	currency VARCHAR(3),
	language VARCHAR(50),
	population INT
);
